resolution: Go to the IAM page, in the left navigation pane click Service Accounts, navigate to your service account and check if it has viewer role attached
If service account has all the required roles/permissions [viewer role or list/get permissions of the failed service], then check if failed service's APIs are enable or not
Go to the APIs & Services page, in the left navigation pane click Enable APIs & Services
Search API and check if it is enable or not, if not then enable the API
Repeat above step for all the mentioned services
